("613","81","FI3476","15","63","<p><b><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">1- João Lucas anda 1</span><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"> m</span><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"> em</span><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"> 2 s</span><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">, qual a velocidade média dele ?</span></b></p><p><b><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><br></span></b></p><p>Observe que já temos duas grandeza, que são : O tempo (2 s) e o espaço (1 m).</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(44, 62, 80); font-family: \" open=\"\" sans\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 17px;=\"\" text-align:=\"\" center;\"=\"\">Para resolver usaremos a fórmula :</span><br></p><p><b><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">﻿Vm</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; line-height: 1; color: rgb(44, 62, 80); font-family: \" open=\"\" sans\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 17px;=\"\" text-align:=\"\" center;\"=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; line-height: 1;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> = </span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; line-height: 1; font-size: 14px;\">ΔS/</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; line-height: 1; font-size: 14px;\">ΔT</span></span></span></b></p><p>Onde:</p><p><b><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Vm = x</span></b></p><p><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; line-height: 1; color: rgb(44, 62, 80); font-family: \" open=\"\" sans\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 14px;=\"\" text-align:=\"\" center;\"=\"\"><b>ΔS = 1 m</b></span></p><p><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; line-height: 1; color: rgb(44, 62, 80); font-family: \" open=\"\" sans\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 17px;=\"\" text-align:=\"\" center;\"=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; line-height: 1; font-size: 14px;\"><b>ΔT = 2 s</b></span></span></p><p><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; line-height: 1; color: rgb(44, 62, 80); font-family: \" open=\"\" sans\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 17px;=\"\" text-align:=\"\" center;\"=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; zoom: 1; line-height: 1;\">Para resolvermos, basta dividir a distancia pelo tempo. Observe :</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(44, 62, 80); font-family: \" open=\"\" sans\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 14px;=\"\" text-align:=\"\" center;=\"\" margin:=\"\" 0px;=\"\" padding:=\"\" zoom:=\"\" 1;=\"\" line-height:=\"\" font-weight:=\"\" 700;\"=\"\">Vm = </span><span style=\"color: rgb(44, 62, 80); font-family: \" open=\"\" sans\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 14px;=\"\" text-align:=\"\" center;=\"\" margin:=\"\" 0px;=\"\" padding:=\"\" zoom:=\"\" 1;=\"\" line-height:=\"\" font-weight:=\"\" 700;\"=\"\">ΔS/</span><span style=\"color: rgb(44, 62, 80); font-family: \" open=\"\" sans\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 14px;=\"\" text-align:=\"\" center;=\"\" margin:=\"\" 0px;=\"\" padding:=\"\" zoom:=\"\" 1;=\"\" line-height:=\"\" font-weight:=\"\" 700;\"=\"\">ΔT</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(44, 62, 80); font-family: \" open=\"\" sans\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 14px;=\"\" text-align:=\"\" center;=\"\" margin:=\"\" 0px;=\"\" padding:=\"\" zoom:=\"\" 1;=\"\" line-height:=\"\" font-weight:=\"\" 700;\"=\"\">Vm = 1 m / 2 s</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(44, 62, 80); font-family: \" open=\"\" sans\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 14px;=\"\" text-align:=\"\" center;=\"\" margin:=\"\" 0px;=\"\" padding:=\"\" zoom:=\"\" 1;=\"\" line-height:=\"\" font-weight:=\"\" 700;\"=\"\">Vm = 0,5m/s</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(44, 62, 80); font-family: \" open=\"\" sans\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 17px;=\"\" text-align:=\"\" center;=\"\" margin:=\"\" 0px;=\"\" padding:=\"\" zoom:=\"\" 1;=\"\" line-height:=\"\" font-weight:=\"\" 700;\"=\"\"><br></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(44, 62, 80); font-family: \" open=\"\" sans\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 17px;=\"\" text-align:=\"\"