("664","70","FI3476","15","64","<p>90 Km/h:3,6=25 m/s</p><p>V=<span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">ΔS/</span><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Δt</span></p><p><font color=\"#222222\" face=\"arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">25 m/s=</span></font><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">ΔS/ 2 s</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">ΔS=25 x 2=<b>50 m</b></span><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><br></span></p>","23-02-2019 1:14","8","1"),
