uanto a distância percorrida será de 210 Km.</span></b></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px;\"><font face=\"Arial\">Determine a velocidade média de um carro que sai Limeira, vai a Ribeirão Preto e retorna a Campinas.</font></span><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><br></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial; font-size: 18px;\">Vm =&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial; font-size: 18px;\">ΔS/&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial; font-size: 18px;\">Δt</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 18px;\"><font face=\"Arial\">Δ</font></span><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">S = Sf - Si</span><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial; font-size: 18px;\"><br></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial; font-size: 18px;\">ΔS = 90 - 150</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: 18px;\"><font face=\"Arial\">Δ</font></span><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">S = -60 m</span><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial; font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial; font-size: 18px;\"><br></span></p><p><b><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial; font-size: 18px;\">Vm = -60/&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial; font-size: 18px;\">Δt</span></b></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial; font-size: 18px;\"><br></span><font face=\"Arial\"><span xss=\"removed\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 14px;\"><br></span></font>                                              
